!}

They come down on the momentum of the spring, and the wave — which has been organizing the same anger from the other direction for twenty years — receives the war's veterans as if it had been waiting for them, which in a sense it had. Whatever the operation cost, it bought this: an entrance into July made not as supplicants but as the people who, that spring, made the regime flinch. The mountain is behind them now. The count is ahead.

@seguir_guerra
new-page: true
face-image: img/muertos.jpg
on-arrival: {!
Q.pres_total = Q.pres_guerrero + Q.pres_chihuahua + Q.pres_valle + Q.pres_jalisco + Q.pres_nl + Q.pres_oaxaca + Q.pres_tijuana;
Q.guerra_fuerza = Q.pres_total + Q.moral_columnas * 0.4 + Q.parque * 1.5 - Q.coronel_red * 0.5 + (Q.coronel_muerto ? 15 : 0) + Q.veteranos * 3 + (Q.auge_armada ? 20 : 0);
if (Q.guerra_fuerza >= 50) { Q.ending = "guerra_larga"; }
else { Q.ending = "exterminio"; }
!}

= El que se queda

The war does not come down the year it finally acted. Let the valley have July; the sierra keeps its own calendar.

[? if ending = "guerra_larga" : Held at strength through the season the country looked away, the war endures the way strong wars endure a distracted enemy: the zones hold, the corridos add their verse, and the state — its hands full of a stolen election — cannot spare the force to finish a war that will not finish itself. It becomes the unfinished business of 1988, the thing neither the counted votes nor the stolen ones resolved, waiting in the mountains for the decade to turn and a new generation to climb up and understand. ?]

[? if ending = "exterminio" : Held past its strength out of the pride the manuals warned against, the war meets, while the country studies its ballot, the end the manuals promised: the last zones swept without witnesses, the columns run to ground, the encirclement closed in the dark on a war too weak to break it. There is no July for the sierra — only the older arithmetic, one camp at a time, and a silence the corridos will spend forty years refusing to accept. ?]

- @fin_seguir: Fin.

@fin_seguir
go-to: finale
